text: Jan Wallén (born 6 June 1935) is a Swedish former sports shooter. He competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Sweden Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Skåne County
